							About Us
							
							





Altisource Asset Management Corporation (“AAMC”) is an asset management company that provides portfolio management and corporate governance services to investment vehicles that own real estate related assets. Its initial client is Altisource Residential Corporation, a real estate investment trust that acquires and operates quality, affordable single-family rental homes throughout the United States.  AAMC’s principal offices are located in the United States Virgin Islands.  AAMC also has operations in the Cayman Islands, Luxembourg and India through its subsidiaries, AAMC Cayman SEZC Ltd., Altisource Consulting S.a r.l. and River Business Solutions Pvt. Ltd., respectively.





 




	Contact Us







				
		36C Strand Street
		Christiansted, VI 00820
                Telephone: 1-340-692-1055 





 












