Real Estate Management Services

REO lifecycle management solutions


 Interested in learning more?
Contact Us 






What we offer
Altisource specializes in marketing and disposition strategies for distressed residential real estate and has sold over 180,000 homes.1 Altisource has developed marketing strategies and industry best practices serving top 10 servicer and bank clients since 2009. We utilize technology-enabled inventory management processes to drive controlled and efficient sales operations to help decrease resolution timelines and loss severity. At the same time, we also maintain the homes to comply with the various investor, agency and local requirements, to reduce neighborhood blight and to help minimize reputational and financial risks for stakeholders.
Available real estate management services include:

Field services 
Asset management
Valuations
Brokerage
Closing and settlement
Title curative services
Title search and grading
Short sale management
HOA identification and dues management
Property registration services
Customized marketing plans
Hubzu® real estate marketplace platform
Eviction services
Occupied property sales
Seller representation 

1as of 12/31/15






Focus on process controls
With expertise managing the stringent requirements of servicer and bank clients, Altisource continuously monitors existing business controls to help mitigate risk and to proactively address emerging industry requirements.






Help increase scale and efficiency
Automation and strict quality controls help to streamline processes and reduce variability in outcomes. 






Offer customized solutions
Real estate management services and process requirements can be customized to meet specific client objectives. 














Over 50,000 REO properties under management*

